<p>IMG Worlds of Adventure is the world''s largest indoor temperature-controlled theme park — covering 1.5 million sq ft in Dubai''s City of Arabia. Marvel heroes, Cartoon Network characters, Dinosaurs, and more — all in powerful air-conditioning regardless of season.</p>
