(
  'Dubai Creek: A Complete Travel Guide',
  'dubai-creek-complete-travel-guide',
  'Complete travel guide to Dubai Creek — abra rides, Gold Souk, Spice Souk, Al Fahidi, dhow dinner cruises and how to get there.',
  '<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1548036328-c9fa89d128fa?w=900&q=80" alt="Dubai Creek traditional dhow boats Deira" style="width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;"/>
<h2>Dubai Creek: A Complete Travel Guide</h2>
<p>Dubai Creek — Khor Dubai — is the soul of old Dubai. This 15 km saltwater inlet shaped the city''s destiny as a trading hub. Dhow boats, spice-scented alleyways, and gold-drenched souks fill every corner.</p>
