</div>
<h2>Tips</h2><ul><li>The AED 1 abra ride is one of Dubai''s best experiences — do not skip it</li><li>Most souks close 1–3 PM on weekdays for a break</li><li>Gold and Spice Souks are walking distance from each other</li><li>Dress modestly in this traditional area</li><li>Best itinerary: Al Fahidi + abra + Gold Souk + dhow dinner cruise</li></ul>
