(
  'Gold Souk Dubai: Visitor Guide & How to Get There',
  'gold-souk-dubai-visitor-guide-how-to-get-there',
  'Complete guide to Gold Souk Dubai — what to expect, how to buy gold, bargaining tips, purity guide, opening hours, and how to reach this iconic market.',
  '<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1610375461246-83df859d849d?w=900&q=80" alt="Gold Souk Dubai glittering jewellery Deira" style="width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;"/>
<h2>Gold Souk Dubai: Visitor Guide &amp; How to Get There</h2>
<p>The Gold Souk in Deira has over 300 shops displaying tonnes of gold jewellery. Dubai gold prices are among the world''s lowest — and all gold is regulated by the government, making this a genuinely safe and rewarding shopping destination.</p>
<h2>Location &amp; Drive Times</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">From</th><th style="padding:10px;">Drive Time</th><th style="padding:10px;">Metro</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Dubai Airport</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">15–20 min</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Green Line → Al Ras</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Downtown Dubai</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">30–35 min</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Red → Green Line</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;">Dubai Marina</td><td style="padding:10px;text-align:center;">40–50 min</td><td style="padding:10px;">Metro + walk</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
