<tr><td style="padding:10px;"><strong>14K</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;">58.3%</td><td style="padding:10px;">Fashion jewellery</td><td style="padding:10px;">Lower</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<div style="background:#fefce8;border:1px solid #fde047;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;margin:16px 0;"><p style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Key Fact — How Pricing Works</p><p style="font-size:14px;">The gold rate per gram is <strong>fixed daily</strong> by the Dubai Gold &amp; Jewellery Group. Shops cannot change this. You negotiate the <strong>making charge</strong> (labour: AED 5–25/g) — that is where your savings happen.</p></div>
<h2>Step-by-Step Buying Guide</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">Step</th><th style="padding:10px;">Action</th><th style="padding:10px;">Why</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">1</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Check daily gold rate online</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Know exact base price per gram</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">2</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Browse 3–4 shops first</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Compare designs and making charges</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">3</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Negotiate making charges</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">This is where savings happen</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">4</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Request hallmark certificate</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Proves purity and authenticity</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;">5</td><td style="padding:10px;">Get full receipt</td><td style="padding:10px;">Keep for customs declarations</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>Opening Hours</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">Day</th><th style="padding:10px;">Hours</th><th style="padding:10px;">Note</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Saturday – Thursday</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">10:00 AM – 10:00 PM</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Break 1–3 PM weekdays</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;">Friday</td><td style="padding:10px;">4:00 PM – 10:00 PM</td><td style="padding:10px;">Closed morning</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>Tips</h2><ul><li>Visit in the evening — beautifully lit and most lively</li><li>Cash gives better bargaining leverage than card</li><li>Souk is covered — comfortable year-round</li><li>Combine with Spice Souk (5 min walk) and a Creek abra ride</li><li>Keep passport copy for high-value purchases</li></ul>
<h2>How to Get There</h2><p>Al Ras Metro Station nearby. For direct airport-to-souk transfers, a private taxi is simpler. <strong>Airport Travel Taxis</strong> serves all Deira destinations. <a href="/booking">Book your ride</a></p>',
