<h2>Al Fahidi Historical District: Everything You Need to Know</h2>
<p>Al Fahidi — also known as Al Bastakiya — is Dubai''s oldest surviving neighbourhood. While the city races skyward, this beautifully preserved quarter of wind towers and ochre courtyards offers something increasingly rare: a genuine connection to old Dubai before the skyscrapers.</p>
